  <brief_title>A Study of ATR-101 for the Treatment of Endogenous Cushing's Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2 Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study of ATR-101 for the Treatment of Cushing's Syndrome</official_title>
